<h1 id="authentication-module">Authentication Module</h1>
<h2 id="tldr">TL;DR</h2>
<p>OAuth2 + session cookie. Three providers wired. Critical path is the
session middleware.</p>
<h2 id="architecture-overview">Architecture Overview</h2>
<pre class="mermaid">
graph TD
  A[routes/auth.ts] --> B[middleware/session.ts]
  B --> C[providers/oauth.ts]
  B --> D[providers/local.ts]
</pre>
<p>The auth module is layered: routes call middleware, middleware
delegates to provider modules.</p>
<h2 id="behavior">Behavior</h2>
<p>The login flow:</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb1"><pre
class="sourceCode typescript"><code class="sourceCode typescript"><span id="cb1-1"><a href="#cb1-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">async</span> <span class="kw">function</span> <span class="fu">login</span>(creds<span class="op">:</span> Credentials)<span class="op">:</span> <span class="bu">Promise</span><span class="op">&lt;</span>Token<span class="op">&gt;</span> {</span>
<span id="cb1-2"><a href="#cb1-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="kw">const</span> provider <span class="op">=</span> providers<span class="op">.</span><span class="fu">resolve</span>(creds<span class="op">.</span><span class="at">kind</span>)<span class="op">;</span></span>
<span id="cb1-3"><a href="#cb1-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  <span class="cf">return</span> provider<span class="op">.</span><span class="fu">issue</span>(creds)<span class="op">;</span></span>
<span id="cb1-4"><a href="#cb1-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>}</span></code></pre></div>
<h2 id="health-risk">Health &amp; Risk</h2>
<ul>
<li>Test coverage thin in <code>providers/local.ts</code></li>
<li>Several <code>// TODO</code> markers around rate limiting</li>
<li>Session secret rotation not implemented</li>
</ul>

      </main>
